'''Deputy Viceroy''' was a position of the [[Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation]]. This position automatically made the holder of the title one of the [[Viceroy of the Trade Federation/Legends|Viceroy's]] [[Advisor/Legends|advisors]] and [[Lieutenant/Legends|lieutenants]]. It was last held by [[Hath Monchar]].

The post was empty due to the death of Monchar. He once was to be next-in-line for [[Viceroy/Legends|Viceroy]]. He had control over all Trade Federation trading posts, but had to be approved by legal counsel [[Rune Haako/Legends|Rune Haako]]. It was unfilled after the betrayal of Hath.

